{"tid":1335812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[必入]假日搭車攻略","createTime":"2019-07-20T16:23:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T10:39:30.000Z","uid":52428,"like":231,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"6e68116f4642b525317c9a299a9319b0dc71cce4","tid":1335812,"uid":52428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:23:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4yCzUoE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4yCzUoE.png&h=41d2a182&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n假日uber攻略：<br />\n上落客位就3-4個司機一齊開Uber app喺附近排隊等客<br />\n揸順風車兜人嘅司機，可以知道邊到可以兜人<br />\n不過順風車就唔好開uber app<br />\n記住係免費，冇錢銀交易<br />\n<br />\n想搭車嘅朋友，唔好咁心急落order<br />\n行過去附近睇吓有冇免費嘅順風車先<br />\n記得上車之前掉咗啲垃圾先<br />\n上到車都唔好唔好亂咁講野<br />\n<br />\n如果個上落客點交通擠塞嘅話<br />\nUber司機就好記得要熄app了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FQ2DBB8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFQ2DBB8.png&h=e7c49857&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"556e4223c2368af69f60e7a5c4fd4e683ba26367","tid":1335812,"uid":52428,"like":119,"dislike":0,"score":119,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RN3Woiq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRN3Woiq.png&h=2bc9fbb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家記得係要登記做Uber driver乘客先會知道你係邊架<br />\n唔好你眼望我眼等人去登記跟大隊呀"},{"pid":"4f0f991ff37eab50fefe2b10c3045c98df6af166","tid":1335812,"uid":71024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:30:57.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"fbec95ae864abb1a693ff0f4ff58f18adfea0887","tid":1335812,"uid":169357,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:33:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9omQsNr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=