 />\nUber司機就好記得要熄app了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FQ2DBB8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFQ2DBB8.png&h=e7c49857&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T21:13:24.000Z","msg":"In <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">LKF/維記</span> we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9c6c692bb6a5c7ffe46c4622ad071062289f01","tid":1335812,"uid":23632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T21:28:28.000Z","msg":"推 <a href=\"https://t.me/hkuber\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkuber&d=5riwYeXkLlljSywqzybc4q7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=19ab2680\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkuber</a>"},{"pid":"ad479d7e7612a577c8182e3a72ef80cdaaf3ae5e","tid":1335812,"uid":159594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T22:46:30.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"88ba8ed2cae5392b964994f0aa7ba76ef2346408","tid":1335812,"uid":159594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T22:51:53.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"03e939a4d8a6a9d993da7e5a7fc05fa92f61fa40","tid":1335812,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6003febbb5c802cc1f45bd08a09ef73adce2061e","tid":1335812,"uid":57274,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:37:55.000Z","msg":"如果狗登記咗做uber司機，再幾個聚係一個點等人到呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T22:53:34.000Z","msg":"狗咁玩野咩<br />\n喺架車度4 條友熔咗佢都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}